{"id": 56994, "date": "2025-06-02T04:00:08", "date_gmt": "2025-06-02T11:00:08", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=56994"}, "modified": "2026-02-15T10:39:36", "modified_gmt": "2026-02-15T18:39:36", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-june-2-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/06/02/kingdom-of-days-june-2-2/", "title": {"rendered": "June 2"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band open for Chicago at the Baltimore Civic Center. Prior to the show, Bruce stops by WHFS-FM in Bethesda for an interview and in-station performance.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NPAVhepem1A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Listen to Bruce recall his memory of this show 36 years later:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KhV6i-sWdBg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band headline at the Agora in Toledo, Ohio. This show is notable for its opener: the only known performance of &#8220;A Night Like This&#8221; (also known as &#8220;Angel Baby&#8221; or &#8220;Dance On Little Angel&#8221;), an outtake that remains unreleased to this day.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iBgH1Irpf2w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Recording continues for Bruce&#8217;s fourth album. Today the band works on &#8220;Rendezvous.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>A year and a day after recording sessions begin, Bruce releases his fourth studio album, <em>Darkness on the Edge of Town</em>. (Thanks to friend of the blog Andy Swanson for the <em>Billboard</em> scan!)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_lDjjM6fhv8UAF1WLd5MyGr39PsIy3DXjs\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"27570\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-06-02a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?fit=299%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"299,960\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1590318286&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-06-02a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?fit=93%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?fit=299%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-27570 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?resize=299%2C960&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"299\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?w=299&amp;ssl=1 299w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1978-06-02a.jpg?resize=93%2C300&amp;ssl=1 93w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 299px) 100vw, 299px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"18775\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-06-02b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?fit=650%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"650,961\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1590318267&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-06-02b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?fit=203%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?fit=650%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-18775 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?resize=650%2C961&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"961\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?w=650&amp;ssl=1 650w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1978-06-02b.jpg?resize=203%2C300&amp;ssl=1 203w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"27572\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/bruce-darkness-review-billboard-jun-24-1978_0001-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?fit=1594%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1594,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Bruce &amp;#8211; Darkness Review Billboard Jun 24, 1978_0001\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?fit=187%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?fit=637%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-27572 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1217&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1217\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?w=1594&amp;ssl=1 1594w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?resize=187%2C300&amp;ssl=1 187w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?resize=637%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 637w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1234&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?resize=956%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 956w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Bruce-Darkness-Review-Billboard-Jun-24-1978_0001-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p>That night, Bruce makes a return visit to the U.S. Naval Academy in Annapolis during the Darkness Tour, and the band tour premieres &#8220;Sea Cruise&#8221; for the occasion.</p>\n<div id=\"v-BynSK9FG-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/BynSK9FG?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>At Night Four at London&#8217;s Wembley Arena, Link Wray guest-stars on &#8220;I Fought the Law.&#8221; In attendance at tonight&#8217;s show: Joe Jackson, Kim Carnes, Elvis Costello, Paul Cook of The Sex Pistols, all of The Pretenders except for Chrissie Hynde, all of the Ants except for Adam, and unnamed members of U2, The Psychedelic Furs, The Fabulous Thunderbirds, and The Members.</p>\n<div id=\"v-ITvqaqNw-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ITvqaqNw?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ibBf1Xvalvg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"35087\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-06-02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1981-06-02.jpg?fit=%2C&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"[]\" data-image-title=\"1981-06-02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1981-06-02.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1981-06-02.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-35087\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1981-06-02.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Recording continues for what will become\u00a0<em>Born in the U.S.A.</em> at The Hit Factory in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce, Roy, Patti, and the Miami Horns join Max Weinberg&#8217;s band Killer Joe on stage at The Stone Pony for four songs.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Z5HLzrqT-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Z5HLzrqT?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"18776\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1989-06-02/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?fit=488%2C963&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"488,963\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1590318647&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1989-06-02\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?fit=152%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?fit=488%2C963&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-18776 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?resize=488%2C963&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"488\" height=\"963\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?w=488&amp;ssl=1 488w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/1989-06-02.jpg?resize=152%2C300&amp;ssl=1 152w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 488px) 100vw, 488px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Reunion Tour to Paris for the first of two nights. Elliott Murphy makes a guest appearance on &#8220;Hungry Heart.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-uFeEsKEc-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/uFeEsKEc?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"51278\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/fort_worth_star_telegram_thu__jun_3__1999_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i