.jpg?resize=1380%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1380w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Fort_Worth_Star_Telegram_Thu__Jun_3__1999_-scaled.jpg?resize=1840%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1840w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Fort_Worth_Star_Telegram_Thu__Jun_3__1999_-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2004:\u00a0</strong>Bruce politely but pointedly declines an invitation to be interviewed by the Los Angeles Times on the occasion of the 50th anniversary of the Fender Stratocaster.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"32381\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1977/02/02/cover-me-apache/bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large.gif?fit=1000%2C1294&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1294\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large.gif?fit=232%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large.gif?fit=758%2C981&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-32381 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/bruce-springsteen-letter-p1-large.gif?resize=758%2C981&#038